name: FrankfurtRestaurants
0:
”Alexa, tell Frankfurt restaurants to recommend me vegan restaurants in Altstadt district”
”Alexa, Open Frankfurt restaurants and I would like to eat sushi in Ostend district”
”Alexa, Open Frankfurt restaurants and tell me where I can eat for 10 Euro”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: frankfurt restaurants
des:
With Frankfurt Restaurant skill, you can search for restaurants, bars, fast-food at a given location. For example, you could say "Sushi in Ostend district". 

You can also add information on how much money you wish to spend for a meal per person, by saying "Pizza for 10 Euro". At any point, you can say stop or exit to finish the Frankfurt Restaurant skill. Say help to get more information on search phrases.

The Frankfurt Restaurant skill has been designed and developed by Ksawery Oksytowicz and Jakub Giza. Please give us your feedback at jakub.giza@spicyscrum.com
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
